<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf0262044-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7918"><num value="7918">§ 7918.</num><heading> Period of effectiveness</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter shall be effective beginning with the 2002 crop year of each covered commodity through the 2007 crop year.</p>
